Beautiful Neighborhood, Golf Course in the back, so NO Rear New Neighbors and NO Front Neighbors, ALL GREEN SPACE.  House needs a little TLC and some Handyman Work!  True Diamond in the Rough with the MAJOR COMPONENTS ALREADY UPDATED AND Completed so Super Easy to Finish with YOUR PERSONAL TOUCHES.  Investors Welcomed and Invited, Long Term Tenants Already in Place and Want to Opportunity to Remain.  Let's Make a Deal and Get this Home SOLD.  Sebring Florida is an AWESOME PLACE TO CALL HOME.  Low Cost of Living.  Stop Renting and Own YOUR OWN HOME.  SCHEDULE YOUR APPOINTMENT to view 3252 GOLFVIEW ROAD, SEBRING, FL.
